Proof of Stake (PoS), low-power blockchain developed in-house and live tested 
in the energy markets during trials in 2016 and 2017. EcoChain has been 
stress-tested in high-load environments and has provided valuable insights 
into blockchain functionality and compatibility, with energy data collection and 
settlement  

