Our goal is for the adoption of the Platform and Ecosystem globally.   

We aim to democratize power: to bring the benefits of our technology to 
consumers leading to lower power bills, better prices for excess renewable 
power, and use of cleaner energy.   

At the same time, we aim to help businesses to host advanced applications and 
services in a rapid, transparent, and profitable way. 

